qmk userspace
==============

Custom QMK keymaps for Kinesis Advantage 2 (kint41).

::

    keyboards/kinesis/kint41/keymaps/danishprakash/

Layers
------

- 0: base QWERTY
- 1: navigation (HJKL arrows, hold Tab/Esc)
- 2: numpad on right keywell (hold LGui)

Setup
-----

::

    qmk config user.overlay_dir="$(realpath ~/code/dotfiles/qmk_userspace)"

Build & flash
-------------

::

    qmk compile -kb kinesis/kint41 -km danishprakash
    qmk flash -kb kinesis/kint41 -km danishprakash
